[Legend of Awakening]

28
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,810
[Episode 36]

29
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:36,399
The Yan Family is famous for its sword techniques.

30
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:40,600
Today my son will inherit the Sword of Yan,

31
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:43,180
as well as Wuji Manor.

32
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:49,280
Congratulations, Young Master!

33
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,700
What's wrong Old White?

34
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,940
Sword.

35
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:08,040
The man with the sword.

36
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:13,760
It was him. He killed my brother.

37
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:23,460
Old White.

38
00:03:23,460 --> 00:03:26,179
Father, who is that?

39
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:30,780
Lu Ping, how come it's you?

40
00:03:30,780 --> 00:03:34,199
Kill him. Kill him. You promised me!

41
00:03:34,199 --> 00:03:35,879
- Old White.
- Kill him.

42
00:03:35,879 --> 00:03:39,860
Turns out it's you. You are the murderer from 19 years ago.

43
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:43,459
Murderer? Master Yan is a murderer? What is going on?

44
00:03:43,459 --> 00:03:46,779
Lu Ping, what are you talking about? Who is he?

45
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:53,999
People from the Mountain and Sea Gang have snuck into the Agile Dragon Army. Get them.

46
00:03:53,999 --> 00:03:58,500
There will be enough time for that later. I, as the son of Leng Xiutan,

47
00:03:58,500 --> 00:04:00,800
will get my justice from you.

48
00:04:02,540 --> 00:04:04,659
- Go.
- Kill him!

49
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,199
A Ze, chase them.

50
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:11,070
[Wuji]

51
00:04:11,070 --> 00:04:13,700
General Wen, what's going on?

52
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:16,560
Ask your respected father later yourself.

53
00:04:22,820 --> 00:04:26,120
[Wuji Manor]

54
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:31,219
Master, we've already taken care of the guests.

55
00:04:31,219 --> 00:04:34,340
But Young Master said he would like to go out for a walk.

56
00:04:34,340 --> 00:04:38,899
- What about Ling Ziyan?
- Miss Ling has been in her room this whole time, hasn't cried or made a fuss.

57
00:04:38,899 --> 00:04:41,380
She said she would wait for Young Master to return.

58
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:43,860
At least she's a sensible girl.

59
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:45,940
What about Young Master?

60
00:04:45,940 --> 00:04:49,780
He is confused. He will be back. You may take your leave.

61
00:04:49,780 --> 00:04:51,080
Yes.

62
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:56,820
Master, we have divided the disciples into a dozen or so teams of men and horses.

63
00:04:56,820 --> 00:05:01,820
They've searched around Wuji Manor, but haven't found any signs of Lu Ping.

64
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:06,320
And County Master Xining seems to be back in camp.

65
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:08,160
She seems to have been hurt.

66
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:11,179
Continue the search. Send all our men

67
00:05:11,179 --> 00:05:14,420
and stop them from gossiping.

68
00:05:14,420 --> 00:05:19,559
We should say it was the plot of Mountain and Sea Gang, that Lu Ping was lured here by Liu Song.

69
00:05:19,559 --> 00:05:21,460
This needs to be the only version of this story.

70
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:22,760
Yes.

71
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,720
Go on then.

72
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,920
Yes.

73
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:41,000
Come on out now.

74
00:05:54,740 --> 00:05:58,160
As my son, you shouldn't be so depressed.

75
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:03,000
Father, don't you think that you owe me an explanation?

76
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,780
You've always had a reason

77
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:12,780
for everything you've done.

78
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:17,080
That year I left home,

79
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:20,260
you never sent anyone to come and find me.

80
00:06:21,660 --> 00:06:24,760
I knew that you wanted me to grow up.

81
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:28,160
But I really don't understand what happened today.

82
00:06:30,020 --> 00:06:34,919
You weren't actually detaining Lu Chenfeng for his own safety were you?

83
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,820
That's right.

84
00:06:36,820 --> 00:06:41,920
What about Lu Ping and Qin Sang? Did you send someone to kill them, to silence them?

85
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:49,039
I should have killed them in person. Then today's troubles would've never happened.

86
00:06:49,039 --> 00:06:54,180
The brother Lu Chengfeng said you killed,

87
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:58,539
was the master of Big Dipper, Leng Xiutan, right? Lu Ping's father?

88
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,400
Yes.

89
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,580
Father.

90
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:16,300
But you said his parents were killed by the Mountain and Sea Gang.

91
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:21,460
That's also correct. I'm the one that started the Mountain and Sea Gang.

92
00:07:25,220 --> 00:07:26,860
I don't understand.

93
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:31,360
Since we've already discussed this much,

94
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:34,940
I might as well tell you everything.

95
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:45,050
More than ten years ago,

96
00:07:45,050 --> 00:07:47,920
Wuji Manor didn't exist in Jianghu.

97
00:07:48,940 --> 00:07:54,800
In Jianghu, only the seven masters of Big Dipper were the most famous.

98
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:08,500
Master Leng Xiutan was excellent at the Pneuma of Sound.

99
00:08:08,500 --> 00:08:11,900
His wife Shao Yinchu was a hero.

100
00:08:11,900 --> 00:08:14,960
She achieved perfection with the sword on her own.

101
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:19,180
I was ranked second through my abilities with the Sword of Yan technique.

102
00:08:19,180 --> 00:08:25,040
The rest, Chu Min and Guo Youdao could use both the Pneuma of Strength and Air.

103
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:34,480
Liu Song was the last to join us.

104
00:08:34,480 --> 00:08:38,739
He was noble, extravagant, and good at the Pneuma of Essence.

105
00:08:42,060 --> 00:08:45,759
Chenfeng was the youngest. He had some mental health issues.

106
00:08:45,759 --> 00:08:49,180
But he was a genius at the Pneuma of Energy.

107
00:08:49,180 --> 00:08:51,200
He was an expert in creating weapons.

108
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:57,100
Brother Leng was kind and amiable.

109
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,880
He was deeply in love with his wife

110
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:04,600
and also took good care of us.

111
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:12,280
We seven were young and in our prime.

112
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:19,480
Once, on my way to see you and your mother,

113
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:22,500
I met His Majesty.

114
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:28,459
He was just a young person then. But his courage and insight were something to be admired immediately.

115
00:09:28,459 --> 00:09:32,040
We talked for an entire night and became close friends.

116
00:09:35,520 --> 00:09:38,300
Brother Yan is skilled in martial arts.

117
00:09:38,300 --> 00:09:42,980
It would be a pity if you don't use your skills to open up new territories.

118
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:49,140
Worthy little brother, you have such ambitions.

119
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:54,560
I will do my best to convince Big Dipper to help you and your father.

120
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:04,880
At that time, the world was a mess, and warlords and heroes were appearing all the time.

121
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:11,480
Everyone wanted to make a name for themselves, including your father.

122
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:15,880
But Brother Leng just didn't think the same.

123
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:36,639
Older Brother, I lost again.

124
00:10:36,639 --> 00:10:39,260
Younger Brother, your sword is vigorous.

125
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:42,560
I don't think it'll be even two years before you'll surpass me.

126
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:48,680
Older Brother, I have something I want to say.

127
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:52,439
There's been so much fighting in the world. These days everyone is vying for supremacy.

128
00:10:52,439 --> 00:10:57,899
It's unbearably chaotic in the Jianghu realm. It's our chance to show our strength.

129
00:10:57,899 --> 00:11:02,300
What if... we got involved?

130
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:06,420
On my way back, I met Zhai Wei and Zhai Rong.

131
00:11:06,420 --> 00:11:09,559
They are leading the uprising. Most people support them.

132
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:14,180
We can help them with the help of people from other sects in Jianghu.

133
00:11:14,180 --> 00:11:17,040
- I believe that in the future-
- Enough.

134
00:11:17,040 --> 00:11:21,620
Don't say any more. I don't agree.

135
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:24,819
Brother, our master taught us all martial arts skills.

136
00:11:24,819 --> 00:11:28,880
Was it just so we could swap useless pointers with each other every day?

137
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:32,040
I have told you many times.

138
00:11:32,040 --> 00:11:35,680
Big Dipper should never interfere in politics.

139
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:38,479
Our mission is to share and pass down martial arts skills.

140
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:42,420
Over the years, no matter how many dynasties there are,

141
00:11:42,420 --> 00:11:45,240
we can have only one Big Dipper.

142
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:50,680
Older Brother, when the world is in chaos, who is able to stay out of it?

143
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:57,180
If people in Jianghu become the hired hands for the courts,

144
00:11:57,180 --> 00:12:00,460
then martial artists will lose their identities.

145
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:06,040
Big Dipper doesn't want to interfere and we can't interfere.

146
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,680
Understood.

147
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:15,259
Older Brother. Older Brother.

148
00:12:15,259 --> 00:12:18,319
Look. I made a suit of armor for Ping'er.

149
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:28,159
Chenfeng, you are now the Master of Tianquan Peak. You can't keep not studying martial arts skills.

150
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:32,819
Brother, it's okay if I can't use martial skills. The Big Dipper still has you here.

151
00:12:32,819 --> 00:12:35,519
How is learning martial arts more meaningful than creating weapons?

152
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:39,319
As long as you're always the master here, then I'll always create weapons for you.

153
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:44,460
Moreover, once Ping'er is older, he'll definitely be more skilled than me.

154
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:46,140
I'll count on him to protect me.

155
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:48,139
Don't let the child fall. Let me.

156
00:12:48,139 --> 00:12:50,220
He's quite strong.

157
00:12:52,340 --> 00:12:55,080
The child was Lu Ping?

158
00:12:55,080 --> 00:13:00,220
That's right. Older Brother was a serious student of martial arts skills.

159
00:13:00,220 --> 00:13:03,040
He didn't care about the secular world.

160
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:06,940
After the birth of such a talented boy,

161
00:13:06,940 --> 00:13:09,500
he only focused on him.

162
00:13:09,500 --> 00:13:13,520
Big Dipper would contribute nothing under his leadership.

163
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:20,560
I was full of youth and vigor and angry back then.

164
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:26,260
It was only because of my painstaking efforts that Big Dipper was at its height.

165
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:30,060
It was only because he was the master

166
00:13:30,060 --> 00:13:33,700
that I couldn't realize my ambitions.

167
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:39,480
Therefore, I kept waiting for my chance;

168
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:44,880
until one day I found out about Liu Song's secret.

169
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,720
Back then, Liu Song had just entered Big Dipper.

170
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:56,500
He didn't elaborate on his identity.

171
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:59,840
I felt he had a noble spirit about him.

172
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:03,620
But also seemed to be hiding a lot of secrets.

173
00:14:03,620 --> 00:14:09,100
Once, I heard him talking with Older Brother.

174
00:14:09,100 --> 00:14:13,780
Today, I was caught by you.

175
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:19,299
I have nothing to say. Kill me if you want.

176
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:27,740
I can forgive you.

177
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:34,040
But Big Dipper's principle is to never interfere with politics.

178
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:37,220
Right now, you have two choices.

179
00:14:37,220 --> 00:14:42,239
One is, you immediately go down the mountain and continue being the Prince of Dan.

180
00:14:42,239 --> 00:14:46,440
But that means from now on you have no connection with Big Dipper ever again.

181
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:49,840
The second is, you stay here

182
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:55,059
and from now onward you are no longer a prince. You are just Song of the sixth peak.

183
00:14:55,059 --> 00:14:58,940
And from then on, Big Dipper will always be with you.

184
00:14:58,940 --> 00:15:03,820
You also would need to hand over the Thousand Pine Ruler and commander's seal

185
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:06,540
to prove your determination to stop the war.

186
00:15:08,400 --> 00:15:09,900
Follow me.

187
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:17,960
After my investigation, Liu Song, the one who claimed he admired martial arts

188
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:20,880
and came to learn martial skills,

189
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:23,310
was actually the Prince of Dan.

190
00:15:23,310 --> 00:15:24,720
[Big Dipper]

191
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:28,460
I knew this was my only chance.

192
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:32,800
So I took the initiative to find Zhai Rong.

193
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:40,660
The time is right.

194
00:15:40,660 --> 00:15:45,360
What did you prepare in exchange for this cup of tea?

195
00:15:46,300 --> 00:15:48,460
Liu Song is at Big Dipper.

196
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:51,839
But Leng Xiutan cares very much about him.

197
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:55,260
As long as he's there, you can't kill Liu Song.

198
00:15:55,260 --> 00:15:59,880
You want the commander's seal? I can get it for you.

199
00:15:59,880 --> 00:16:02,140
Then what do you want in return?

200
00:16:02,140 --> 00:16:05,440
A chance for a new start.

201
00:16:18,540 --> 00:16:20,280
It's a deal.

202
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:24,760
At the time, Big Dipper always opened its doors

203
00:16:24,760 --> 00:16:28,580
to all the sects in Jianghu to discuss martial arts.

204
00:16:28,580 --> 00:16:32,359
In order to get the seal, I took advantage of when Older Brother and his wife

205
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:38,120
took Ping'er down the mountain and drew away Chu Min and Guo Youdao.

206
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:41,780
Only Liu Song and Chenfeng were left on the mountain.

207
00:16:42,500 --> 00:16:47,940
I pretended to leave, saying I was going to see you and your mother.

208
00:16:51,100 --> 00:16:56,359
Zhai Rong and his men disguised themselves as a sect and came in.

209
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:58,600
They took the opportunity to take the seal.

210
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:00,020
[Big Dipper]

211
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:02,500
So as not to make them suspicious,

212
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:07,440
I gave the sect, that Zhai Rong disguised their group as, a name:

213
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:09,760
the Mountain and Sea Gang.

214
00:17:13,319 --> 00:17:17,979
If Uncle Leng and them had already left. Why did they suddenly come back?

215
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:20,800
Was it you that…

216
00:17:22,160 --> 00:17:26,800
Yes. The seal was locked in the Seven Martyr Court.

217
00:17:26,800 --> 00:17:31,459
How could we obtain it so easily? A fight was inevitable.

218
00:17:31,459 --> 00:17:35,940
I knew Brother Leng and his wife, in order to suppress Luping's natural six pneumas,

219
00:17:35,940 --> 00:17:38,199
must have lost a lot of their cultivation.

220
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:42,360
I purposely asked for their help to lure them back.

221
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:45,120
Leng Xiutan, hearing Liu Song was in danger,

222
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:48,420
hurried back before he was fully recovered.

223
00:17:48,420 --> 00:17:53,320
Thanks to Lu Ping, I was able to take them down in one move.

224
00:17:53,320 --> 00:17:54,840
Father.

225
00:17:56,520 --> 00:18:01,560
They retreated from Astronomical Observatory all the way to Seven Martyr Court.

226
00:18:02,120 --> 00:18:05,640
They thought I was there to come to the rescue.

227
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:08,360
He never put his guard up around me.

228
00:18:09,220 --> 00:18:10,500
- Brother. Sister.
- Qiuci.

229
00:18:10,500 --> 00:18:12,059
My wife and I will guard this place.

230
00:18:12,059 --> 00:18:16,120
You go to the secret room to help Song and Ping'er and take them away.

231
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:02,920
Brother.

232
00:19:05,980 --> 00:19:08,980
Brother. Brother!

233
00:19:17,390 --> 00:19:19,950
[Big Dipper]

234
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:28,000
Brother, don't worry.

235
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,480
I will be better than you.

236
00:19:33,520 --> 00:19:36,800
I shouldn't have let Lu Chengfeng live.

237
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:41,260
But I had already killed Brother Leng and his wife.

238
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:43,740
I couldn't bear

239
00:19:45,860 --> 00:19:48,940
to kill my junior.

240
00:19:48,940 --> 00:19:51,480
I had no intention to kill them all.

241
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:56,400
But I couldn't let him go and risk spreading the truth.

242
00:19:57,020 --> 00:20:00,840
I locked him up in the water prison at Wuji Manor.

243
00:20:00,840 --> 00:20:03,780
I destroyed his memory with drugs.

244
00:20:04,660 --> 00:20:09,980
I told people he was out traveling around and that his whereabouts were unknown.

245
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:24,760
So you knew from the beginning that Liu Song was behind the Mountain and Sea Gang.

246
00:20:25,480 --> 00:20:26,860
Yes, that's right.

247
00:20:26,860 --> 00:20:30,920
I just didn't think that he had gotten so good at the Pneuma of Essence.

248
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:34,460
Surprisingly, he even created diversions to dodge my men as they searched for him.

249
00:20:34,460 --> 00:20:40,200
I never thought they would've hidden the seal in the Thousand Pine Ruler.

250
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:43,460
Didn't you get the Thousand Pine Ruler back?

251
00:20:43,460 --> 00:20:46,719
Can't you let Lu Ping and the others go? Don't make any more mistakes.

252
00:20:46,719 --> 00:20:49,080
We can't let the truth get out.

253
00:20:49,080 --> 00:20:52,560
Otherwise, the reputation of Wuji Manor will be destroyed.

254
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:56,859
He is my brother. He is the son of your older brother.

255
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:03,080
Dead men tell no tales.

256
00:21:04,220 --> 00:21:06,980
Father, you didn't teach me to be like this.

257
00:21:06,980 --> 00:21:11,640
Since childhood, I was taught to be a straightforward and upright hero.

258
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:13,340
Heroes shouldn't be like this.

259
00:21:13,340 --> 00:21:15,720
How am I not straight forward and upright?!

260
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:20,080
I single-handedly brought peace among all the disputes these past few years.

261
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:23,840
I even protected the border

262
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:26,880
by building Wuji Manor in Jin City.

263
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:30,700
I earned my position as the Master of Jianghu through my own two hands.

264
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:32,740
My conscience is clear.

265
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:40,460
The position shows both my ambition and my responsibility.

266
00:21:42,320 --> 00:21:47,799
But you started all this by killing and trapping your brothers and fellow disciples.

267
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:51,660
Now the ones killing people are the Mountain and Sea Gang.

268
00:21:51,660 --> 00:21:56,640
If it weren't for me, the Mountain and Sea Gang would be a hundred times more rampant than it is now!

269
00:21:56,640 --> 00:22:01,700
All of Jianghu could have been cut into pieces and swallowed up as separate territories.

270
00:22:01,700 --> 00:22:02,959
Father.

271
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:06,980
I can live up to the position as a master of martial arts.

272
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:12,420
This world will always need a hero.

273
00:22:12,420 --> 00:22:15,720
Not just me. You will be one, too.

274
00:22:17,060 --> 00:22:21,460
Father, I beg you. Lu Ping is my brother through life and death.

275
00:22:22,020 --> 00:22:26,779
Zhao Xifan can be merciful. You, Yan Xifan cannot.

276
00:22:27,600 --> 00:22:30,700
You are the successor of the master of martial arts circles.

277
00:22:30,700 --> 00:22:33,480
For the sake of the future,

278
00:22:33,980 --> 00:22:36,580
you have to think this through thoroughly.

279
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:49,760
Master, you really are clever.

280
00:22:49,760 --> 00:22:54,260
After I sent that item over, something happened at Wuji Manor.

281
00:22:54,260 --> 00:22:56,180
Lu Chenfeng created a tremendous uproar at the wedding.

282
00:22:56,180 --> 00:23:00,160
Now, he and Lu Ping are on the run.

283
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:04,820
Is the item still with Yan Qiuci?

284
00:23:04,820 --> 00:23:08,439
Yes. He can't bear to let it go.

285
00:23:09,760 --> 00:23:14,720
[Mountain Sea]

286
00:23:18,420 --> 00:23:21,140
After so many years,

287
00:23:21,140 --> 00:23:23,700
it seems like he hasn't changed.

288
00:23:24,380 --> 00:23:26,660
Help me prepare well.

289
00:23:26,660 --> 00:23:31,380
This grace, I have to repay my second brother in person.

290
00:23:31,880 --> 00:23:33,160
Yes.

291
00:24:16,460 --> 00:24:18,020
Why?

292
00:24:22,260 --> 00:24:24,280
Young Master Xifan.

293
00:24:24,280 --> 00:24:26,120
Why?!

294
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:37,360
Young Master Xifan, we don't have time to indulge in sadness.

295
00:24:37,360 --> 00:24:41,399
We have to think about how to make this a win-win situation. Stop Master Yan from killing Lu Ping.

296
00:24:41,399 --> 00:24:45,179
Otherwise, both of them will suffer. Then the Mountain and Sea Gang will have gotten everything they wanted.

297
00:24:45,179 --> 00:24:48,420
In the end, only our loved ones are sad, while the hated ones are happy.

298
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:56,180
Ziyan, can you help me?

299
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:10,379
Master. Younger Master…

300
00:25:11,040 --> 00:25:16,320
One has to sacrifice something in order to do something big. Give him some time and he will understand.

301
00:25:16,320 --> 00:25:18,059
All right. What's next?

302
00:25:18,059 --> 00:25:21,660
Continue to search for Lu Ping and Lu Chenfeng.

303
00:25:21,660 --> 00:25:24,600
I will go meet with Princess Xining.

304
00:25:31,960 --> 00:25:35,019
Princess, Master Yan has arrived.

305
00:25:35,019 --> 00:25:38,200
Princess Xining.

306
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:43,999
Wen Rui, I have something to talk to Master Yan about.

307
00:25:43,999 --> 00:25:45,099
Leave us.

308
00:25:45,099 --> 00:25:47,419
- Princess.
- Leave us.

309
00:25:48,840 --> 00:25:50,240
Yes.

310
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:04,620
Yan Qiuci, you unscrupulous dog.

311
00:26:06,660 --> 00:26:08,780
You escaped from death.

312
00:26:08,780 --> 00:26:13,460
I didn't think to come and get payback but instead searched for Lu Ping.

313
00:26:13,460 --> 00:26:18,300
You didn't leak any information to your closest lieutenant general either.

314
00:26:19,760 --> 00:26:22,940
I would boldly hazard a guess

315
00:26:23,980 --> 00:26:29,799
that when you were in the water prison, you had already figured it out.

316
00:26:29,800 --> 00:26:31,880
That the events 19 years ago regarding the Seven Peaks, had something to do with not only me,

317
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:37,240
but also His Majesty.

318
00:26:38,680 --> 00:26:41,300
Master Yan, you have a lot of tricks.

319
00:26:41,300 --> 00:26:43,620
You, Princess, are clever.

320
00:26:43,620 --> 00:26:45,920
I could never understand why

321
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:49,440
His Majesty treated Lu Ping so strangely.

322
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:53,620
He wanted to make Lu Ping an official but he was still guarded around him.

323
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:59,340
All the evidence can be linked. It was the only explanation.

324
00:27:01,460 --> 00:27:05,120
Now the entire alliance against the Mountain and Sea Gang

325
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:10,080
is supported by Wuji Manor. The arrow is already on the string.

326
00:27:10,080 --> 00:27:13,480
Princess, as a loyal woman,

327
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:16,440
you should know the benefit and the harm.

328
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:19,740
I warn you. I will find Lu Ping.

329
00:27:19,740 --> 00:27:24,620
But if you dare hurt him, I will destroy all of Wuji Manor as payment.

330
00:27:45,600 --> 00:27:48,740
Lu Ping, wait for me.

331
00:27:55,540 --> 00:27:57,379
Master, wait for me!

332
00:27:57,379 --> 00:27:58,860
Qin Sang.

333
00:28:03,240 --> 00:28:04,640
Where is my brother?

334
00:28:04,640 --> 00:28:06,159
Why are you two here?

335
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:10,379
We found a way to break the pneuma confinement in Wuyou Valley and came to tell my brother.

336
00:28:10,379 --> 00:28:12,879
Why? Isn't he with you?

337
00:28:13,880 --> 00:28:19,430
Stop talking about Lu Ping. She looks a little off. Let me check your pulse first.

338
00:28:19,430 --> 00:28:23,400
Don't rush to check my pulse. You came at just the right time.

339
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:25,560
Let's go find Lu Ping together.

340
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:46,340
This… This…

341
00:28:46,340 --> 00:28:48,000
What is it?

342
00:28:51,060 --> 00:28:52,460
No.

343
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:03,519
Thank you, Ziyan.

344
00:29:03,519 --> 00:29:06,680
Let's hope the effects last until we're done with everything.

345
00:29:11,600 --> 00:29:16,700
Father, you taught me to be upright and straightforward since I was a child.

346
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:20,080
To be a brave hero.

347
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:24,100
I hope that you will always be that hero.

348
00:29:24,720 --> 00:29:29,400
The mistakes you've made in the past, I will make up for you.

349
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:35,900
I just hope you won't hate me later.

350
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:13,660
Old White,

351
00:30:15,840 --> 00:30:17,780
I didn't take good care of you well enough.

352
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:22,440
I am afraid.

353
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:26,620
Don't be afraid Uncle. I am Ping'er.

354
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:30,160
Ping'er.

355
00:30:31,040 --> 00:30:36,140
After Ping'er grows up, he'll definitely be more skilled than I am. Then I can count on him to protect me.

356
00:30:36,140 --> 00:30:40,120
- Don't let the child fall.
- He is quite strong.

357
00:30:41,500 --> 00:30:43,400
Who is Ping'er?

358
00:30:48,580 --> 00:30:53,059
- How long has it been?!
- How long has it been since you took the medicine? Have you regained your memory?

359
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:07,060
Brother. Brother.

360
00:31:07,060 --> 00:31:11,080
Sister-in-Law. Where is Sister-in-Law?

361
00:31:11,760 --> 00:31:13,160
Brother.

362
00:31:13,920 --> 00:31:16,320
Your brother wants you to eat properly.

363
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:19,760
Get some good rest.

364
00:31:20,980 --> 00:31:25,120
And the bad guy? What about the bad guy?

365
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:29,060
Don't worry. Brother will help you take care of him.

366
00:31:30,080 --> 00:31:31,580
Brother!

367
00:31:38,060 --> 00:31:39,260
Are you okay?

368
00:31:39,260 --> 00:31:42,510
I urged Mo Lin to hurry, but we were still late.

369
00:31:42,519 --> 00:31:45,579
Why are you blaming me again? I almost broke my legs from all the running.

370
00:31:45,579 --> 00:31:49,480
I am okay. It's just that I found out some information.

371
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,860
Why are two you here?

372
00:31:51,860 --> 00:31:55,520
We were in Wuyou Valley and accidentally learned from my father that

373
00:31:55,520 --> 00:31:59,659
the pneuma confinement on you was created by your parents and my father.

374
00:31:59,659 --> 00:32:03,600
And your parents lost most of their cultivation because of it.

375
00:32:03,600 --> 00:32:07,050
I thought it was strange. So I wanted to tell you immediately.

376
00:32:07,579 --> 00:32:09,900
Lost most of their cultivation…

377
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:13,280
Don't kill me.

378
00:32:16,020 --> 00:32:18,640
Boss, who is he?

379
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:23,479
I have to go take care of something. Take care of Old White.

380
00:32:27,040 --> 00:32:30,640
Don't kill me. Don't kill me.

381
00:32:33,760 --> 00:32:36,660
Lu Ping, I have something to tell you.

382
00:32:37,520 --> 00:32:42,900
You can't stay at Wuji Manor. Take Su Tang, Mo Lin, and Lu Chengfeng back to Big Dipper.

383
00:32:42,900 --> 00:32:45,420
I will ask Wen Rui to cover you.

384
00:32:45,420 --> 00:32:48,480
Yan Qiuci wanted to kill us yesterday to keep us quiet.

385
00:32:49,040 --> 00:32:51,880
You're surrendering to him today?

386
00:32:51,880 --> 00:32:56,760
I didn't surrender. We need Wuji Manor to eliminate the Mountain and Sea Gang.

387
00:32:56,760 --> 00:32:58,160
I understand.

388
00:32:59,294 --> 00:33:01,074
It is for the bigger picture.

389
00:33:01,714 --> 00:33:03,960
The Mountain and Sea Gang killed Qin Qi.

390
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:06,960
Are you willing to let them go?

391
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:16,420
If for the bigger picture we can't tell right from wrong anymore,

392
00:33:16,420 --> 00:33:19,319
then what are we protecting?

393
00:33:19,320 --> 00:33:21,160
- Lu Ping.
- Qin Sang.

394
00:33:22,700 --> 00:33:24,560
I'm not like you.

395
00:33:25,800 --> 00:33:30,180
I can clearly tell right from wrong. Please go back.

396
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:36,720
Lu Ping, Yan Qiuci is Xifan's father.

397
00:33:36,720 --> 00:33:38,960
If you kill him, will it bring back your parents?

398
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:42,130
Aren't you afraid that the gang will be more rampant if you kill him?

399
00:33:46,100 --> 00:33:51,380
I am a nobody. I can't think about that much.

400
00:33:52,380 --> 00:33:55,280
And I don't have the energy to think about it. If you block me again—

401
00:33:55,280 --> 00:33:56,940
Then what?

402
00:34:21,180 --> 00:34:22,800
Are you okay?

403
00:34:30,620 --> 00:34:34,219
You've been poisoned. The poison has already started to attack your heart.

404
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:39,120
Don't tell anyone.

405
00:35:05,540 --> 00:35:10,620
Let's talk at midnight in the manor. Uncle Yan.

406
00:35:16,100 --> 00:35:20,220
- Young Master, you mean…
- Do you need me to say it again?

407
00:35:20,220 --> 00:35:25,099
Tonight all the disciples will return to their rooms. Don't light the lanterns. Don't go out.

408
00:35:25,099 --> 00:35:30,600
Anyone who disobeys will be dispelled from the manor. Understand?

409
00:35:30,600 --> 00:35:32,600
But Master ordered that…

410
00:35:32,600 --> 00:35:38,120
He ordered that everyone listens to my orders.

411
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:39,540
Yes, Sir.

412
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:48,100
What are you planning to do?

413
00:35:58,360 --> 00:36:02,260
Ziyan, get some sleep.

414
00:36:02,260 --> 00:36:06,560
When you wake up, everything will have been taken care of.

415
00:36:21,970 --> 00:36:26,560
[Wuji Manor]

416
00:36:51,630 --> 00:36:55,330
[Wuji Manor]

417
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:56,240
Are you here to stop me?

418
