When you were in Zhaifeng, did you ever succeed?

421
00:38:11,160 --> 00:38:17,740
I know that you never give up once you've made up your mind.

422
00:38:17,740 --> 00:38:19,960
I'm the one that has to be accommodating.

423
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:21,940
I'm sorry.

424
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:28,440
As the son of my parents, I have to hold someone accountable.

425
00:38:31,620 --> 00:38:36,020
Lu Ping, Father is waiting for you inside.

426
00:38:36,020 --> 00:38:40,640
Later on, I'll need your help with the battle against the Mountain and Sea Gang.

427
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:11,340
[Wuji]

428
00:39:32,460 --> 00:39:34,120
You've come.

429
00:39:34,120 --> 00:39:38,940
