431
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:47,700
Yes.

432
00:39:47,700 --> 00:39:52,440
Did you attack me and Qin Sang, and imprison us in the water prison?

433
00:39:53,040 --> 00:39:54,440
Yes.

434
00:40:00,680 --> 00:40:05,280
Back then the death of your parents was indeed my fault.

435
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:10,800
