439
00:40:21,100 --> 00:40:23,380
I did it involuntarily.

440
00:40:23,380 --> 00:40:25,960
But now that I've got the Thousand Pine Ruler,

441
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:31,000
I believe that you will be able to bring an end to the disaster caused by the Mountain and Sea Gang.

442
00:40:31,000 --> 00:40:34,620
Today, I promise to accept three of your moves.

443
00:40:34,620 --> 00:40:39,679
Whether I live or die, I'll leave it up to fate. After three moves, I hope you will forget the hatred.

444
00:40:39,679 --> 00:40:43,540
And cooperate with Wuji Manor against Liu Song.

445
00:40:43,540 --> 00:40:46,480
My father's Horn is very powerful.

